  "prompt": "Which are the top software companies in Ahmedabad for .net developers?",
  "response": "Ahmedabad has emerged as a significant hub for IT and software development companies in India, including many that focus on .NET development. While the landscape can change over time, as of the latest information available in 2023, here are some well-regarded software companies in Ahmedabad that often seek .NET developers:\n\n1. **Tatvasoft**: A prominent software development company, Tatvasoft offers a variety of services, including custom .NET development. They serve clients globally and have a strong presence in Ahmedabad.\n\n2. **Yudiz Solutions**: Known for innovative solutions and a wide range of services, Yudiz Solutions often hires for .NET development roles among others.\n\n3. **OpenXcell**: This company specializes in custom software development and has a good reputation for utilizing .NET technologies to deliver robust solutions.\n\n4. **Cygnet Infotech**: With a focus on technology and innovation, Cygnet Infotech provides diverse IT solutions, including .NET development, to clients around the world.\n\n5. **Peerbits**: Known for mobile and web app development, Peerbits also employs .NET developers to facilitate end-to-end software solutions.\n\n6. **KCS (Krish Compusoft Services)**: KCS offers a variety of IT services and frequently works on projects involving .NET frameworks.\n\n7. **Simform**: A high-quality tech service provider, Simform delivers web and mobile solutions with a strong backbone of .NET development expertise.\n\n8. **Prompt Softech**: This company focuses on delivering technological solutions across various sectors and utilizes .NET among other technologies for their projects.\n\n9. **Hidden Brains**: With vast experience in software development, Hidden Brains offers custom .NET solutions to meet diverse client needs.\n\n10. **SmartFish Designs**: While primarily known as a design agency, SmartFish Designs also integrates .NET technologies into their software solutions.\n\nThese companies are known for their work environment, opportunities for growth, and innovative projects. However, it's always recommended to carry out additional research or directly contact these companies for current job openings and specific details about their projects.",
